<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 08:09:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>6 名青少年因涉嫌参与 2020 年斩首法国教师事件而受审</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-28/ty-article/6-teenagers-go-on-trial-for-their-alleged-role-in-the-2020-beheading-of-a-french-teacher/0000018c-14d3-d19a-a3cf-7cd326180000</link><description>塞缪尔·帕蒂 (Samuel Paty) 是一名历史和地理教师，于 2020 年 10 月 16 日在巴黎西北部郊区的学校附近被一名变得激进的 18 岁车臣裔青少年杀害。袭击者随后被警方击毙</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 07:40:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-28/ty-article/6-teenagers-go-on-trial-for-their-alleged-role-in-the-2020-beheading-of-a-french-teacher/0000018c-14d3-d19a-a3cf-7cd326180000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正确地怀疑哈马斯将延迟释放人质归咎于“技术问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-rightly-doubts-hamas-when-its-blames-technical-issues-for-delays-freeing-hostages/0000018c-12b3-d65f-a7dd-f2f7f1140000</link><description>显而易见，哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔正试图采用“饥饿游戏”式的心理战：利用各种借口拆散父母子女、兄弟姐妹，只允许其中部分人返回以色列。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 04:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-rightly-doubts-hamas-when-its-blames-technical-issues-for-delays-freeing-hostages/0000018c-12b3-d65f-a7dd-f2f7f1140000</guid></item><item><title>11 名人质从加沙获释；以色列收到另外 10 人名单，将于周二公布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-live/11-hostages-freed-from-gaza-israel-receives-list-of-10-more-to-be-released-on-tuesday/0000018c-1405-dd2e-a5ae-d74f01bf0000</link><description>11 名以色列妇女和儿童被哈马斯扣押 52 天后从加沙获释 ■ 以色列和哈马斯同意将停火期限再延长两天 ■ 84 岁以色列人质获释后入院治疗，生命垂危 ■ 至少 1,200 人自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内有平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有 200 多名人质被