5 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-cannot-blame-antisemitism-alone-for-global-condemnation/0000018c-127f-dd2e-a5ae-d37f2f890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列右翼剥夺巴勒斯坦权力机构合法性的运动是哈马斯获胜的方式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-rights-campaign-to-delegitimize-the-pa-is-how-hamas-will-win/0000018c-1294-dd2e-a5ae-d3dfde8c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 22:33:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-rights-campaign-to-delegitimize-the-pa-is-how-hamas-will-win/0000018c-1294-dd2e-a5ae-d3dfde8c0000</guid></item><item><title>太多男人持枪：战争导致家庭暴力增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/too-many-men-with-guns-war-brings-out-an-increase-in-domestic-violence/0000018c-1295-dd03-a7ff-bebdc30b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 22:33:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/too-many-men-with-guns-war-brings-out-an-increase-in-domestic-violence/0000018c-1295-dd03-a7ff-bebdc30b0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日大屠杀后的第二天，哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔在加沙地带隧道会见了以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-sinwar-met-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-strip-tunnels/0000018c-12d6-d65f-a7dd-f2d75b9f0000</link><description>以色列高级官员确认已达成协议，将为期四天的休战再延长两天，以换取另外 20 名人质获释</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 22:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-sinwar-met-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-strip-tunnels/0000018c-12d6-d65f-a7dd-f2d75b9f0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日大屠杀发生前几个月，以色列情报部门收到了令人不寒而栗的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/chilling-warnings-picked-up-by-israeli-intelligence-months-before-october-7-massacre/0000018c-1261-dd2e-a5ae-d36ba6240000</link><description>以色列军事情报局的一名士官在 10 月 7 日之前的几个月里发出了 3 次警告，称哈马斯正准备对加沙边境附近的以色列社区发动袭击，但她的话被置若罔闻</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 20:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/chilling-warnings-picked-up-by-israeli-intelligence-months-before-october-7-massacre/0000018c-1261-dd2e-a5ae-d36ba6240000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯停火、人质换囚犯协议再延长两天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-cease-fire-hostage-for-prisoner-deal-extended-for-two-more-days/0000018c-120c-d2ae-afcf-37de94510000</link><description>哈马斯和以色列均证实有报道称，他们已同意将停火协议延长到周一的最后期限之后，“条件与原始协议相同”。美国希望推动进一步暂停战斗天数</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 19:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-cease-fire-hostage-for-prisoner-deal-extended-for-two-more-days/0000018c-120c-d2ae-afcf-37de94510000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙地带与哈马斯的战争中，以色列抗焦虑药物的使用激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/use-of-anti-anxiety-medicine-soars-in-israel-amid-war-with-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018c-11b7-d2ae-afcf-35f7785e0000</link><description>Clalit HMO 表示，与前一个月相比，10 月份镇静剂和精神科药物的处方数量猛增了 11%。 Maccabi HMO 报告上涨了 20%。 “大多数人都会与专业人士交谈，但如果有人无法正常工作，我们会给他们药物。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 19:10:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/use-of-anti-anxiety-medicine-soars-in-israel-amid-war-with-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018c-11b7-d2ae-afcf-35f7785e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对埃隆·马斯克的令人厌恶的拥抱是对犹太人（无论是死的还是活的）的愤世嫉俗的背叛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-27/ty-article/.highlight/israels-repulsive-embrace-of-elon-musk-is-a-cynical-betrayal-of-jews-dead-and-alive/0000018c-11d4-d65f-a7dd-f1d707c80000</link><description>张开双臂欢迎这样一位有毒的大亨，并带他参观在他任内遭到贬低、贬低和否认的大屠杀地点，这应该是内塔尼亚胡遗产上的一个污点</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 18:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-27/ty-article/.highlight/israels-repulsive-embrace-of-elon-musk-is-a-cynical-betrayal-of-jews-dead-and-alive/0000018c-11d4-d65f-a7dd-f1d707c80000</guid></item><item><title>佛蒙特州伯灵顿男子因涉嫌仇恨犯罪枪杀三名巴勒斯坦学生而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-shooting-three-palestinian-students-in-u-s-in-suspected-hate-crime/0000018c-117f-dd03-a7ff-bf7fd9da0000</link><description>枪击事件发生之际，穆斯林和阿拉伯裔美国人的权利和倡导团体报告称，针对阿拉伯人和穆斯林美国人的仇恨犯罪史无前例地激增</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-shooting-three-palestinian-students-in-u-s-in-suspected-hate-crime/0000018c-117f-dd03-a7ff-bf7fd9da0000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯裔以色列人质逃离哈马斯囚禁，在当地人抓住他之前躲在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/russian-israeli-hostage-escaped-hamas-captivity-hid-in-gaza-before-locals-caught-him/0000018c-1121-dd2e-a5ae-d36bfcc40000</link><description>俄罗斯裔以色列人罗尼·克里沃伊 (Roni Krivoi) 是迄今为止唯一获释的成年男性人质，他成功逃离哈马斯几天，但最终在周日被抓获并释放回以色列</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/russian-israeli-hostage-escaped-hamas-captivity-hid-in-gaza-before-locals-caught-him/0000018c-1121-dd2e-a5ae-d36bfcc40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名人​​权组织敦促国际刑事法院对哈马斯的强奸和其他性犯罪行为进行调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israeli-rights-group-urges-icc-probe-of-hamas-for-rape-and-other-sex-crimes/0000018c-1168-dd03-a7ff-bf78860e0000</link><description>这份由以色列人权医生组织发表的论文提供了哈马斯 10 月 7 日涉嫌性犯罪和基于性别的犯罪的详细清单，这些犯罪已被记录并公开分享。根据已知的情况，该文件得出的结论是，此类暴行“普遍存在”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israeli-rights-group-urges-icc-probe-of-hamas-for-rape-and-other-sex-crimes/0000018c-1168-dd03-a7ff-bf78860e0000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质让我们得以一睹加沙哈马斯俘虏的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-offer-glimpse-of-life-in-gaza-as-hamas-captives/0000018c-10fc-d679-abdc-96fcf16d0000</link><description>与 40 名获释人质的家人的对话提供了他们在加沙经历的第一批细节。大多数人被关在隧道里，而其他人则被关在房屋和建筑物中，并担心遭到炮击。有人听到了一项特别的公告来纪念他的九岁生日</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 15:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-offer-glimpse-of-life-in-gaza-as-hamas-captives/0000018c-10fc-d679-abdc-96fcf16d0000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列儿童从加沙获释后开始分享他们的经历</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-from-gaza-israeli-children-held-hostage-by-hamas-begin-to-share-their-experiences/0000018c-10e1-d679-abdc-96f9d9590000</link><description>一些人质返回失去亲人的家庭、无家可归的家庭和支离破碎的社区，同时继续为仍被哈马斯扣押的亲人的安全感到焦虑</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 15:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-from-gaza-israeli-children-held-hostage-by-hamas-begin-to-share-their-experiences/0000018c-10e1-d679-abdc-96f9d9590000</guid></item><item><title>“战争永远是地狱”：道德哲学家谈以色列在加沙行动的伦理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/war-is-always-hell-moral-philosophers-on-the-ethics-of-israels-battle-with-hamas/0000018c-10b8-d2ae-afcf-35fabe230000</link><description>上个月，牛津大学的40多名学者谴责了以色列国防军在加沙的行动，引发了六位以色列道德哲学家的反驳。在那次交流之后，专家们讨论了战争中什么是“相称的”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 14:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/war-is-always-hell-moral-philosophers-on-the-ethics-of-israels-battle-with-hamas/0000018c-10b8-d2ae-afcf-35fabe230000</guid></item></channel></rss>